results.title: Ant-Man (2003) #1
results.description:
Size does matter.  And no one knows this more than Hank Pym - a.k.a. Ant-Man. Got a problem with Galactus? Call the FF. Got a problem with, say, mind-controlled cockroaches? Then Ant-Man's your man! And needless to say, it's done a number on our diminutive hero's self-esteem.  When Ant-Man is tapped to infiltrate an international spy ring that has been siphoning secrets out of Washington, he jumps at the chance - unaware that he's being used as a pawn in a larger game of espionage.
32 PGS./PARENTAL ADVISORY...$2.99
